tion, and a couple other posts have presented supporting data.\u00A0 Other than that, this thread has spiraled out of control.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe need to wait till \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002266485\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SQUAD\u003C/a\u003E( \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167737-uomocapra/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167737\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167737-uomocapra/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@UomoCapra\u003C/a\u003E \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149302\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Darth Badie\u003C/a\u003E ) make their statement.\u00A0 Until then, It is nothing other than supposition and accusations.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"invision","CreatedById":178900,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-09T16:22:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhmmm and here i thought me and squad had very similar taste, turns out they were stealing my ship builds this whole time.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr. Peabody","CreatedById":173591,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-09T16:23:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t you simply stop it from transmitting by switching the internet connection off on your computer or router?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u002